Now that I know the province has changed, I need to search through "Other Resolutions" for any information about "Xã Tân Minh" and "Huyện Ý Yên," specifically within the new province of Ninh Bình. I'm looking for any resolutions that specifically merge or change "Xã Tân Minh."

I'm keeping my eyes peeled, reading each resolution carefully, looking for that specific district and ward name. "1666/NQ-UBTVQH15" mentions "Tân Minh", but it's in Hưng Yên.  Similarly, "1669/NQ-UBTVQH15" mentions "Tân Minh" in Hải Phòng.  No luck so far.

Based on this review of the current resolutions, there is no mention of "Xã Tân Minh" within the relevant region. I need to continue my search through available resources to confirm that there has been no change in the administrative unit for "Xã Tân Minh."
